      <section eId="sec_53_11_5">
        <num>53-11-5</num>
        <content>
          <p>On the motion of any party in interest or on its own motion, the probate court may direct any additional service of citation or other notice or extend the time to respond with respect to any proceedings covered by this chapter as the judge may determine to be proper in the interests of due process and reasonable opportunity for any party or interest to be heard.</p>
